          "title": "Hymn to Inanna",
          "content": "<poem>\n𒀭𒈹 𒌷𒀭𒈹𒆠\n𒂗𒃶𒁺𒀭𒈾\n\nnin me šar₂-ra\nu₆ di-di\n\nMy lady of all the divine powers,\nresplendent light...\n</poem>"
